---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Screen from '../components/Screen.astro';
---

<Layout title="OTA Declaration" wide={true}>
  <Screen>
    <div class="manifesto-container">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="120px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="monolith-logo">
        <path d="M 25 25 A 35.35 35.35 0 1 0 75 25" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="8" stroke-linecap="square"/>
        <rect x="46" y="5" width="8" height="60" fill="#FFFFFF"/>
      </svg>

      <h1>The Open To All (OTA) Declaration</h1>
      <p class="version"><strong>Version:</strong> 1.0</p>
      
      <h2>0. Preamble</h2>
      <p>The Open To All (OTA) movement is built on a single, immutable axiom: knowledge is non-rivalrous and must not be artificially constrained. OTA extends the Free Software movement's framework to all forms of educational, scientific, and structural information.</p>

      <h2>1. The Core Freedoms:</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Freedom 0 (Access):</strong> To access, read, and ingest the material without financial or institutional barriers.</li>
        <li><strong>Freedom 1 (Study):</strong> To study the structural logic, methodology, and underlying data.</li>
        <li><strong>Freedom 2 (Redistribution):</strong> To mirror, host, and redistribute copies to ensure preservation.</li>
        <li><strong>Freedom 3 (Modification):</strong> To translate, adapt, or build upon the material, provided derivations do not impose downstream restrictions.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. Public Domain Dedication</h2>
      <p>This document and the OTA symbol ("The Ascendant Monolith") are dedicated to the public domain (CC0 equivalent). No trademark or copyright is claimed over the geometric paths.</p>

      <h2>3. Implementation</h2>
      <p>To apply the OTA framework, include a copy of this declaration within the root directory (e.g., <code>OTA.md</code>) or embed a direct reference in the metadata of the document.</p>
    </div>
  </Screen>
</Layout>

<style>
  .manifesto-container {
    background-color: var(--screen-bg);
    color: #eeeeee;
    font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, Consolas, monospace;
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding: 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .monolith-logo {
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem auto;
  }

  .manifesto-container h1 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .version {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: #aaaaaa;
  }

  .manifesto-container h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed #444;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .manifesto-container p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: justify;
  }

  .manifesto-container ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .manifesto-container ul li {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    text-align: justify;
  }

  .manifesto-container ul li::before {
    content: ">>";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #888;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .manifesto-container strong {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .manifesto-container code {
    background-color: #111111;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
    border: 1px solid #333;
    border-radius: 3px;
    color: #ffffff;
  }
</style>
